<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="17300000t" end="71100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">进入正题之前先说一点引言  亦或是一些注意事项吧</font></p>
<p begin="74000000t" end="131100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝啊  吾接下来要讲述的是创造第一个眷属时的故事</font></p>
<p begin="133600000t" end="148600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝可不能嫉妒哦</font></p>
<p begin="157400000t" end="183700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好了  从哪儿开始说呢</font></p>
<p begin="187000000t" end="210400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊  就先从事情的经过开始说起吧</font></p>
<p begin="214100000t" end="245000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾来到日本这个国度的经过</font></p>
<p begin="252100000t" end="297500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当时是全盛期中的最盛期  最盛期中的再生期</font></p>
<p begin="302500000t" end="346800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">来日本之前  吾还去过南极  因为想看极光嘛</font></p>
<p begin="351800000t" end="376400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是就结果来说还是失败了</font></p>
<p begin="381400000t" end="413500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  其实也不是因为受不了寒冷</font></p>
<p begin="416400000t" end="452700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">问题在于南极根本就没有人生存</font></p>
<p begin="457700000t" end="504400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没有了目击证词和亲身经验  怪异传说也就无法成立了</font></p>
<p begin="509800000t" end="561100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对着企鹅和白熊再怎么发挥吾的不死之身和怪物性</font></p>
<p begin="563200000t" end="597000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">它们也不可能把我当成话题来传播不是嘛</font></p>
<p begin="602000000t" end="667500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">即便不会被冻死  怎么说呢  我还是感到自己的存在逐渐变弱</font></p>
<p begin="670800000t" end="712100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">噢  这可不妙啊  是大危机啊  吾如此想道</font></p>
<p begin="718800000t" end="763400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">于是便慌张地逃离了南极  用「推摇杆大跳跃」逃了出来</font></p>
<p begin="718800000t" end="798900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（来源：<font face="DFMaruGothic-Md"><font size="28"><b>レバー入れ大パンチ</b></font></font>，本意为推摇杆重拳，源于CAPCOM《恶魔战士》中萨贝鲁的技能，<br />由于出招硬直过大容易造成危险，后产生「<font face="DFMaruGothic-Md"><font size="28"><b>レバー入れ大ピンチ</b></font></font>」（推摇杆大危机）的衍生用法。）</font></p>
<p begin="767600000t" end="796800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？凭丧神小姑娘的跳跃？</font></p>
<p begin="804300000t" end="830200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那种东西根本无法和吾的能力同日而语嘛</font></p>
<p begin="832700000t" end="850200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果把吾的跳跃说得形象一点</font></p>
<p begin="850600000t" end="883500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">起跳的反作用力差点就把南极的大地给毁了</font></p>
<p begin="888500000t" end="925300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当时反正也是随便一跳  估计也就落到海里</font></p>
<p begin="927800000t" end="959900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">正好顺便游游泳清爽一下</font></p>
<p begin="966500000t" end="1016600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是谁料落下的地方  居然是这个国家的地盘</font></p>
<p begin="1027400000t" end="1041600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾掉到了一座湖里</font></p>
<p begin="1045000000t" end="1082100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就在那时  就在吾让这座湖整个消失的时候</font></p>
<p begin="1082900000t" end="1097500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">故事便开始了</font></p>
<p begin="1103800000t" end="1130500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">无聊的  鬼的故事</font></p>
<p begin="1103800000t" end="1130500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">无聊的  鬼的<font size="36">物语</font></font></p>
<p begin="1140000000t" end="1239700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="36"><b>{\an8}本字幕仅供交流试看之用，如您喜欢本作品，请支持购买正版。<br />若因私自散布传播造成法律及相关一切问题，华盟字幕社概不负责。</b></font></p>
<p begin="1140000000t" end="1239700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="36"><b>{\an8}翻译：wjsjwr、酱小鱼；校对：痛爱的飞鱼；<br />歌词协力：信哉；后期：snow；繁化：阿爽。</b></font></p>
<p begin="1739700000t" end="1769300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（第忍话  忍与时间  其二）</font></p>
<p begin="1785200000t" end="1842300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我说汝啊  汝知道吾从南极大跳跃入湖时会发生些什么吗</font></p>
<p begin="1847300000t" end="1897400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  水会飞溅起来  湖里的水几乎全部都溅了起来</font></p>
<p begin="1901100000t" end="1927000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后溅起又落下的水又会怎样呢</font></p>
<p begin="1929500000t" end="1977500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">即使暂时会天空中飞舞  最后还是会受重力影响落到地面</font></p>
<p begin="1979600000t" end="1990400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">以「雨」的形态</font></p>
<p begin="1997100000t" end="2058000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当时这座湖周边受到长期日照  日照之强烈已造成地面干裂</font></p>
<p begin="2063400000t" end="2091800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我只是偶然地让那个地区下了场雨</font></p>
<p begin="2096300000t" end="2139300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从结果来看  吾不但拯救了许多条生命</font></p>
<p begin="2141000000t" end="2195200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">更是拯救了以湖周边为中心的一大片范围内的芸芸众生</font></p>
<p begin="2201900000t" end="2258600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后不巧的是  这个偶然的一刻居然就被目击到了</font></p>
<p begin="2264000000t" end="2300700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">偏偏就是这个「奇迹」发生的瞬间</font></p>
<p begin="2311600000t" end="2368700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说来汝啊  汝知道人类是怎么称呼「奇迹」的制造者吗</font></p>
<p begin="2376600000t" end="2414600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对  奇迹的制造者被称为「神」</font></p>
<p begin="2419200000t" end="2488000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">正确地说  奇迹的制造者  无论是怪异还是人  都被视作「神」</font></p>
<p begin="2518800000t" end="2566800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">于是乎那座湖似乎就变成了什么信仰的对象</font></p>
<p begin="2571000000t" end="2641500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">周边的人们把那座湖作为「神之湖」来崇拜  来祈祷  也就是祈雨</font></p>
<p begin="2647300000t" end="2694900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在那些人看来  吾就是从湖里突然诞生出来的</font></p>
<p begin="2698600000t" end="2733600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就好像湖中的湖水变化成了吾的样子一样</font></p>
<p begin="2739100000t" end="2789500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对当时的日本人来说  突然出现了这么个金发金眼身材修长的人物</font></p>
<p begin="2791600000t" end="2812500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也难怪他们把你当成神仙</font></p>
<p begin="2812500000t" end="2817900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（把小忍当成了神）</font></p>
<p begin="2817900000t" end="2822100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但是）</font></p>
<p begin="2822100000t" end="2828700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（但是……）</font></p>
<p begin="2831200000t" end="2863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是那种状况肯定不会持续多久对吧</font></p>
<p begin="2865900000t" end="2876300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？为什么</font></p>
<p begin="2879200000t" end="2900900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个嘛…从你的性格考虑</font></p>
<p begin="2904200000t" end="2935900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你根本不是那种只是被敬仰信奉就满意的类型吧</font></p>
<p begin="2938400000t" end="2944700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为你是……</font></p>
<p begin="2939700000t" end="2942200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（瞬息万变…）</font></p>
<p begin="2942200000t" end="2943900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（难以捉摸…）</font></p>
<p begin="2943900000t" end="2949300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（…的鬼）</font></p>
<p begin="2943900000t" end="2949300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（只有这一点不会改变的吸血鬼）</font></p>
<p begin="2951800000t" end="2999700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">正像汝所说的那样  这样的神仙生活并没有持续很久</font></p>
<p begin="3003900000t" end="3021800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">差不多将近一年吧</font></p>
<p begin="3025200000t" end="3084000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">且不说吾的性格  可以确定的是吾并不适合做神</font></p>
<p begin="3119000000t" end="3159100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">八九寺真宵就躺在我们的旁边  还没有恢复意识</font></p>
<p begin="3173700000t" end="3214500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那些笨蛋们把吾当成神来祭祀的时候</font></p>
<p begin="3217000000t" end="3258300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾之所以那样顺水推舟  其实也因为正好想休息一下</font></p>
<p begin="3263300000t" end="3309200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不管怎么说都已经被当成神了  住所和食物也自不必愁</font></p>
<p begin="3314200000t" end="3336700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">感觉就像是度假一样</font></p>
<p begin="3343000000t" end="3399300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾的寝宫准确说是做出来的  就在那座消失了的湖泊的湖底</font></p>
<p begin="3405100000t" end="3446900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">换句话说就是建了个神社  建了个非常奢华的建筑</font></p>
<p begin="3454400000t" end="3500200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？汝说吾在这么贫困的村落里还要求人家建造神社</font></p>
<p begin="3500200000t" end="3519400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说吾是个无情的神？</font></p>
<p begin="3525300000t" end="3536900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那可是吾自己建造的</font></p>
<p begin="3541900000t" end="3574900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">难道汝忘记了吗  吾那将物质实体化的能力</font></p>
<p begin="3578200000t" end="3635400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且当时吾处于全盛期  建筑物及其附属一眨眼的工夫就做出来了</font></p>
<p begin="3640000000t" end="3685800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说汝啊  别就穿着一条内裤蹲在那边  吾都看不下去了</font></p>
<p begin="3687900000t" end="3707900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就给汝做件衣服汝快把它穿上好了</font></p>
<p begin="3720500000t" end="3748000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  感觉不错  很合适很合适</font></p>
<p begin="3759200000t" end="3785100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾好歹也尽心尽责地做过神该做的工作</font></p>
<p begin="3788900000t" end="3824300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且雨这种东西也不是下了一次就万事大吉的</font></p>
<p begin="3827200000t" end="3878500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾就每隔一段时间就降了几次雨  随便聚几朵乌云就降了</font></p>
<p begin="3884400000t" end="3909000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说惬意还确实蛮惬意舒服的</font></p>
<p begin="3914000000t" end="3946900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其说是消磨时间倒不如说是享受时间</font></p>
<p begin="3951100000t" end="4019500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当时只是想着只要一直让人们「目击」到吾的话  存在力就能恢复</font></p>
<p begin="4024900000t" end="4060400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然而令人遗憾的是  这并未能如愿</font></p>
<p begin="4065400000t" end="4150900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为吾并不是作为「吸血鬼」这种怪异被「目击」  当然是不会恢复的</font></p>
<p begin="4154600000t" end="4177200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾注意到这一点也花了不少时间</font></p>
<p begin="4183400000t" end="4227600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其实不作为吸血鬼被人目击也没什么关系</font></p>
<p begin="4229300000t" end="4260200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">反正也不是火烧眉毛的问题</font></p>
<p begin="4264800000t" end="4299800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真正的问题在于吾是一直作为「神」被人「目击」的</font></p>
<p begin="4306000000t" end="4326900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和恶魔玩久了就会变成恶魔</font></p>
<p begin="4331500000t" end="4362400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被叫做神叫久了就会变成神</font></p>
<p begin="4366500000t" end="4384000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一直没有主意到这一点的吾…</font></p>
<p begin="4387400000t" end="4429900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  是对此一无所知的吾  真是太糊涂了</font></p>
<p begin="4435800000t" end="4469100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在想来  被当作神的状况吾根本就不应该去接受</font></p>
<p begin="4470800000t" end="4519600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在得知当地没有吸血鬼传说的时候就该赶紧走人</font></p>
<p begin="4525800000t" end="4592200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「一直假扮神明会遭到天谴」  可以单纯地就这样解释</font></p>
<p begin="4600900000t" end="4625100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">至少那家伙是这么说的</font></p>
<p begin="4636000000t" end="4671400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那家伙  没错  就是吾的第一个眷属</font></p>
<p begin="4677700000t" end="4706900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是妖刀心渡的持有者</font></p>
<p begin="4713500000t" end="4748600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个男人一直在战斗  就在那么和平的</font></p>
<p begin="4750200000t" end="4791900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">某种意义上来说比现在还要和平的时代里  在战斗</font></p>
<p begin="4799500000t" end="4809000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝问吾和什么战斗？</font></p>
<p begin="4813200000t" end="4853300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果说他不会和人战斗的话  那么战斗的对象就十分有限了</font></p>
<p begin="4860800000t" end="4882500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  就是和怪异战斗</font></p>
<p begin="4905800000t" end="4943800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和怪异战斗？哎？也就是说他也是专家吗</font></p>
<p begin="4947500000t" end="4950000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不  不对）</font></p>
<p begin="4950000000t" end="4953800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（说是「战斗」总觉得哪里不对）</font></p>
<p begin="4953800000t" end="4955900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（倒不如说是）</font></p>
<p begin="4955900000t" end="4971300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（历/结论）</font></p>
<p begin="4958400000t" end="4969600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吸血鬼猎人</font></p>
<p begin="4973800000t" end="4992100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吧  就是那么回事</font></p>
<p begin="4996300000t" end="5036400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">以消灭妖怪为职业血缘正统的嫡系一族的末裔…</font></p>
<p begin="5043400000t" end="5073100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾也不记得他是不是这么说的了</font></p>
<p begin="5075600000t" end="5121900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">到这儿差不多该把第一个眷属的名字说出来了吧</font></p>
<p begin="5125590000t" end="5150200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">否则我根本无法想象他的样子</font></p>
<p begin="5157300000t" end="5206900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾哪知道  吾本来就对人间界的专有名词记忆模糊</font></p>
<p begin="5209900000t" end="5229900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且也不会去叫谁的名字</font></p>
<p begin="5236590000t" end="5239900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这也太冷血了吧）</font></p>
<p begin="5239900000t" end="5242000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（铁血）</font></p>
<p begin="5242000000t" end="5245300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（热血）</font></p>
<p begin="5245300000t" end="5248200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（都去哪里了）</font></p>
<p begin="5249900000t" end="5315400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾一直叫那家伙「怪异杀手」  就像现在人们这么称呼吾那样</font></p>
<p begin="5322100000t" end="5359600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为他拿着刀很容易和别人区分开来</font></p>
<p begin="5363400000t" end="5385500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且他还有专家所特有的气质</font></p>
<p begin="5388800000t" end="5432600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么为了方便起见就叫他「初代怪异杀手」吧</font></p>
<p begin="5432600000t" end="5435100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（初代怪异杀手）</font></p>
<p begin="5435100000t" end="5438800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（第一个眷属）</font></p>
<p begin="5461800000t" end="5518900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然是消灭妖怪的专家的话  可以理解成是来消灭你的吧</font></p>
<p begin="5522300000t" end="5562700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从某处听到了你的传言  特意过来解决你</font></p>
<p begin="5566100000t" end="5607300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  不是的不是的  虽然有过一次战斗</font></p>
<p begin="5609000000t" end="5648200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是那家伙可不是为了消灭吾而来的</font></p>
<p begin="5652400000t" end="5727500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">想想看  他所听到的传言  也应该是吾被当做神明来祭拜的故事</font></p>
<p begin="5730800000t" end="5755800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">根本不是应该被消灭的对象</font></p>
<p begin="5770400000t" end="5798400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那家伙只是姑且先来看看情况</font></p>
<p begin="5799600000t" end="5835100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">湖泊突然间消失的同时并有神明显灵</font></p>
<p begin="5835500000t" end="5886800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">听到了这种事情  身为「血缘正统」的他  怎会坐视不理呢</font></p>
<p begin="5891800000t" end="5923900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说来那家伙是坐着轿子来的</font></p>
<p begin="5926000000t" end="5980600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">随从浩浩荡荡地跟在后面  宛如大名的队伍那般阵势</font></p>
<p begin="5985200000t" end="6047800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从轿子下来的男人带着的一长一短两把刀吸引了吾的注意力</font></p>
<p begin="6053200000t" end="6075300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">长的一把就是妖刀「心渡」</font></p>
<p begin="6077400000t" end="6106200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">汝用过的那把就是它的复制品</font></p>
<p begin="6109900000t" end="6150400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">第二把妖刀  那把小太刀的名字叫「梦渡」</font></p>
<p begin="6158700000t" end="6179200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那把小太刀究竟是怎样的一把刀呢？</font></p>
<p begin="6182500000t" end="6236300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果说「心渡」是杀怪异的刀  那么小太刀就是用来杀人的吗</font></p>
<p begin="6238800000t" end="6264300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是那样的话  它不就只是一把刀而已嘛</font></p>
<p begin="6266800000t" end="6280900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那是「怪异医师」</font></p>
<p begin="6282600000t" end="6288400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（怪异杀手）</font></p>
<p begin="6285500000t" end="6324300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小太刀「梦渡」是让怪异复生的刀</font></p>
<p begin="6288400000t" end="6293400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（怪异医师）</font></p>
<p begin="6293400000t" end="6299700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（无论什么样的刀　都无法割离它们）</font></p>
<p begin="6326000000t" end="6380600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">让本来没有生命的怪异复生  这说起来也有些奇怪</font></p>
<p begin="6385200000t" end="6416500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之这就是一把让怪异复生的刀</font></p>
<p begin="6426900000t" end="6460700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在那之后那家伙就定期地来巡视</font></p>
<p begin="6461900000t" end="6497800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和吾说些话就回去了  如此反复</font></p>
<p begin="6502400000t" end="6565400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾也帮助过他消灭过一些妖怪  也就在那时建立了信任关系</font></p>
<p begin="6569100000t" end="6619600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说小忍  既然这样你倒不如就这么成为神明不也挺好的嘛</font></p>
<p begin="6625000000t" end="6668800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">听你说来  你倒也是那样的人才  非常的合适</font></p>
<p begin="6673000000t" end="6740600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也不虐待百姓  要说有问题的话  就是你的吸血冲动了吧</font></p>
<p begin="6742200000t" end="6749300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（小忍  声音/台词）</font></p>
<p begin="6742200000t" end="6789800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">白痴  有那个吸血冲动的问题就已经足够了</font></p>
<p begin="6799400000t" end="6802300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真是顽固啊）</font></p>
<p begin="6806000000t" end="6843600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再说了  问题还不止那些</font></p>
<p begin="6857800000t" end="6908200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾身为怪异  吾身为吸血鬼这个存在本身就是问题</font></p>
<p begin="6915300000t" end="6981600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾身为怪异  姬丝秀忒·雅赛劳拉莉昂·刃下心的存在  会聚集怪异</font></p>
<p begin="6987100000t" end="7043800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且聚集过来的  比起怪异更多的是构不成怪异的负能量</font></p>
<p begin="7048000000t" end="7064600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是所谓的「不好的东西」</font></p>
<p begin="7070500000t" end="7095900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是的  是吾大意了</font></p>
<p begin="7101300000t" end="7176000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾不能在一块地方停留太久  因为会打破该地区怪异的生态平衡</font></p>
<p begin="7182700000t" end="7254000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">之所以这样都怪之前住在南极这个人类和怪异都不存在的地方</font></p>
<p begin="7260200000t" end="7316100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个地方根本不会聚集「不好的东西」  而吾却完全没有注意到</font></p>
<p begin="7323600000t" end="7352800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">注意到事情发生的是附近的居民</font></p>
<p begin="7359500000t" end="7372000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">传闻是这样的</font></p>
<p begin="7374900000t" end="7387500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「人消失了」</font></p>
<p begin="7387500000t" end="7392500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「人不见了」）</font></p>
<p begin="7394500000t" end="7413300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「出去了就再也没回来」</font></p>
<p begin="7413300000t" end="7418300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「不见了踪影」）</font></p>
<p begin="7420000000t" end="7465000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然吾和初代怪异杀手讨论过  也一起搜查过</font></p>
<p begin="7468400000t" end="7528000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果却因为没有任何证据  于是便归结于可能是人类犯下的罪行</font></p>
<p begin="7533400000t" end="7553900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就不是吾等的工作了</font></p>
<p begin="7551400000t" end="7554300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不是「神」和「专家」的工作）</font></p>
<p begin="7555100000t" end="7571000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而是警察的工作</font></p>
<p begin="7571000000t" end="7576000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（得出了这样的结论）</font></p>
<p begin="7577600000t" end="7605600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之  吾什么都没做</font></p>
<p begin="7610200000t" end="7629800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是居民还是不断地消失</font></p>
<p begin="7631500000t" end="7662300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">附近的居民还是不断地下落不明</font></p>
<p begin="7670700000t" end="7701100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">直到一个人也不剩为止</font></p>
<p begin="7747400000t" end="7788300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">呃  「一个人都不剩」指的是什么呢</font></p>
<p begin="7792400000t" end="7811200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从你的语气和说话方式中</font></p>
<p begin="7814100000t" end="7857100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我只能理解成周边的居民都不见了</font></p>
<p begin="7860000000t" end="7870400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是这样</font></p>
<p begin="7872900000t" end="7903000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">整个村子的人都失踪了</font></p>
<p begin="7904200000t" end="7905900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（规模太大了）</font></p>
<p begin="7905900000t" end="7908400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（实在是）</font></p>
<p begin="7908400000t" end="7910100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（究竟有多少人失踪了啊？）</font></p>
<p begin="7912100000t" end="7941300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">接下来吾走遍了周围所有的村子</font></p>
<p begin="7944700000t" end="7949700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是吗</font></p>
<p begin="7954300000t" end="7986400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后通过这次探索吾发现</font></p>
<p begin="7988900000t" end="8029800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">周围的村子也都一个人也不剩了</font></p>
<p begin="8034800000t" end="8052300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如同划好了界线一般</font></p>
<p begin="8054800000t" end="8091900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从某处开始  之外的村子都平安无事</font></p>
<p begin="8092700000t" end="8094800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（界线）</font></p>
<p begin="8094000000t" end="8104800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">界线</font></p>
<p begin="8094800000t" end="8095700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（意大利语：界线）</font></p>
<p begin="8095700000t" end="8096500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（界线）</font></p>
<p begin="8096500000t" end="8097300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（德语：界线）</font></p>
<p begin="8097300000t" end="8098200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（葡萄牙语：界线）</font></p>
<p begin="8098200000t" end="8099000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（俄语：界线）</font></p>
<p begin="8099000000t" end="8099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（西班牙语：界线）</font></p>
<p begin="8099800000t" end="8104000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（分界）</font></p>
<p begin="8107800000t" end="8162000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说划分界线的根据就是有没有信奉你吗</font></p>
<p begin="8164900000t" end="8197400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  分得再准确一点的话</font></p>
<p begin="8198300000t" end="8220000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是以「知不知道吾」为界线</font></p>
<p begin="8221200000t" end="8235800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和信仰无关</font></p>
<p begin="8233700000t" end="8235400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没有人的村子）</font></p>
<p begin="8235400000t" end="8237100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（空无一人的村子）</font></p>
<p begin="8237100000t" end="8239100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（——她）</font></p>
<p begin="8248300000t" end="8277500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后吾终于注意到了</font></p>
<p begin="8279200000t" end="8316300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">尽管吾长期停留在这里</font></p>
<p begin="8319200000t" end="8349700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但负面能量却完全没有积攒起来</font></p>
<p begin="8356800000t" end="8372200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">要是说有原因的话</font></p>
<p begin="8373400000t" end="8394700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾想肯定是因为吾在这里停留了太久</font></p>
<p begin="8396000000t" end="8431800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个负面能量已经在某个地方引发了什么事件吧</font></p>
<p begin="8434300000t" end="8450200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但吾在周围转了一圈</font></p>
<p begin="8451900000t" end="8469400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">却并没有发现类似的事件</font></p>
<p begin="8475200000t" end="8491100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没有发生这种事件</font></p>
<p begin="8492300000t" end="8511500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这一点很奇怪  十分异常</font></p>
<p begin="8513200000t" end="8525700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">绝对是异常状态</font></p>
<p begin="8530300000t" end="8546100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说实话  对于吾来说</font></p>
<p begin="8547400000t" end="8578200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">比起周围的居民全都消失了这件事</font></p>
<p begin="8579100000t" end="8624500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾更为周围没有聚集起任何东西这件事而感到不可思议</font></p>
<p begin="8625400000t" end="8637900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">甚至有些感到恐怖</font></p>
<p begin="8660400000t" end="8691300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为感到恐怖  所以吾就回家睡觉了</font></p>
<p begin="8703400000t" end="8706700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">喂</font></p>
<p begin="8710000000t" end="8747100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎？  不舒服的时候最好的办法不就是老老实实地睡觉吗</font></p>
<p begin="8747100000t" end="8758400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然确实是这样！</font></p>
<p begin="8760900000t" end="8765900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（竹○○（割爱））（原文是哆拉A梦里的竹蜻蜓）</font></p>
<p begin="8760900000t" end="8806800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后  正当吾忘了个一干二净准备去睡回笼觉的时候</font></p>
<p begin="8809300000t" end="8835600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">妨碍吾睡觉的家伙却出现了</font></p>
<p begin="8838500000t" end="8848100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">出现了是指…</font></p>
<p begin="8850600000t" end="8862300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">敌人出现了吗</font></p>
<p begin="8854800000t" end="8856800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（敌人）</font></p>
<p begin="8856800000t" end="8857700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（敌人）</font></p>
<p begin="8857700000t" end="8858500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（法语：敌人）</font></p>
<p begin="8858500000t" end="8859300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（意大利语：敌人）</font></p>
<p begin="8859300000t" end="8860200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（德语：敌人）</font></p>
<p begin="8860200000t" end="8861000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（西班牙语：敌人）</font></p>
<p begin="8861000000t" end="8861800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（俄语：敌人）</font></p>
<p begin="8861800000t" end="8865200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「黑暗」）</font></p>
<p begin="8866400000t" end="8873500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是的</font></p>
<p begin="8876000000t" end="8906100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">出现的是「初代怪异杀手」</font></p>
<p begin="8921500000t" end="8962400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所谓的新情报是关于怪异杀手部下的</font></p>
<p begin="8967800000t" end="8983600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他们也都消失了</font></p>
<p begin="8985700000t" end="9004900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不知道消失到什么地方去了</font></p>
<p begin="9008700000t" end="9049500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">等初代怪异杀手回过神来他已经变成孤身一人了</font></p>
<p begin="9054500000t" end="9089200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">于是听了他的描述之后</font></p>
<p begin="9068300000t" end="9072500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（他和吾不同）</font></p>
<p begin="9082100000t" end="9086200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（很有危机感）</font></p>
<p begin="9090800000t" end="9109200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「那就不得不调查一下了呢」</font></p>
<p begin="9095800000t" end="9100000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（而且比危机感更强烈的）</font></p>
<p begin="9107900000t" end="9112100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（是恐惧感）</font></p>
<p begin="9109200000t" end="9125000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾用一副认真的表情这么说道</font></p>
<p begin="9128800000t" end="9177600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽然吾已经在周围的村子转了一圈掌握了现状</font></p>
<p begin="9179700000t" end="9223000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但吾还是陪同初代怪异杀手再次调查了各个村子</font></p>
<p begin="9228000000t" end="9248900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当然村子的状况没有任何变化</font></p>
<p begin="9251800000t" end="9296400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">失踪的人们并没有突然间回来</font></p>
<p begin="9306900000t" end="9329400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">事情就是在这不凑巧的时候发生的</font></p>
<p begin="9326900000t" end="9329400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（突然）</font></p>
<p begin="9329400000t" end="9333200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（出现了）</font></p>
<p begin="9335200000t" end="9352800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾们调查了最后一个村子</font></p>
<p begin="9355300000t" end="9392400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当确认最后一间房子里也没有人后</font></p>
<p begin="9396500000t" end="9425700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">初代怪异杀手真是要多消沉有多消沉</font></p>
<p begin="9428200000t" end="9453300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就在他纤细的心灵受到伤害的时候</font></p>
<p begin="9457400000t" end="9476200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那东西出现了</font></p>
<p begin="9482500000t" end="9506200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就是汝所说的「黑暗」</font></p>
<p begin="9512100000t" end="9526300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">毫无征兆地</font></p>
<p begin="9528300000t" end="9545900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在大白天就出现了</font></p>
<p begin="9555900000t" end="9558000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（终于出现了）</font></p>
<p begin="9558000000t" end="9561700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（进入正题了）</font></p>
<p begin="9574600000t" end="9608800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说实话  吾一开始还以为那是什么自然现象</font></p>
<p begin="9616800000t" end="9665100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽说吾觉得用「黑色的一团」来描述是最合适的</font></p>
<p begin="9669700000t" end="9708900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但它似乎又并没有「团结」成「一团」的样子</font></p>
<p begin="9716000000t" end="9724400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">被吞了进去</font></p>
<p begin="9729000000t" end="9741900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾们两个都被吞了进去</font></p>
<p begin="9748600000t" end="9767800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这就是那些人消失的原因吗</font></p>
<p begin="9770700000t" end="9793200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当吾发现的时候已经太迟了</font></p>
<p begin="9799500000t" end="9827800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾全身上下大约四分之三都已经被吞了进去</font></p>
<p begin="9833200000t" end="9873300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过留下四分之一也够了</font></p>
<p begin="9875400000t" end="9887500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">足够用来逃跑了</font></p>
<p begin="9892500000t" end="9919600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾一路飞到了南极</font></p>
<p begin="9901200000t" end="9905400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（啊  这不是在逃跑  这不是在逃跑）</font></p>
<p begin="9914100000t" end="9916700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（吾有生以来）</font></p>
<p begin="9920000000t" end="9922900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（从来没有逃跑过）</font></p>
<p begin="9923300000t" end="9973800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就算是吾  也是第一次在肉体上受到如此大的损伤</font></p>
<p begin="9975500000t" end="9993800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之吾想和它保持距离</font></p>
<p begin="9999200000t" end="10016300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但从结果上来说</font></p>
<p begin="10016300000t" end="10038000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其实没必要做到这一步</font></p>
<p begin="10041800000t" end="10067600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为那片「黑暗」并没有追过来</font></p>
<p begin="10071800000t" end="10086800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不管吾等了多久</font></p>
<p begin="10092200000t" end="10123100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就这样吾离开了日本</font></p>
<p begin="10125200000t" end="10149800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后就再也没有回来</font></p>
<p begin="10155200000t" end="10193600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾再次到访日本便要追溯到半年前</font></p>
<p begin="10199900000t" end="10233600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">并且在那时遇到了汝</font></p>
<p begin="10250300000t" end="10262800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？  等一下</font></p>
<p begin="10266190000t" end="10285400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">初代怪异杀手最后怎么样了</font></p>
<p begin="10294500000t" end="10307900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾不是说了吗</font></p>
<p begin="10309500000t" end="10333290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他和吾一起被「黑暗」吞噬了</font></p>
<p begin="10335790000t" end="10353800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾只被吞噬了四分之三</font></p>
<p begin="10355790000t" end="10392100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但先被吞进去的他可就不止这样了</font></p>
<p begin="10397100000t" end="10413390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">几乎全身都被吞进去了</font></p>
<p begin="10416700000t" end="10429700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这不是很奇怪吗  小忍</font></p>
<p begin="10432600000t" end="10462200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果那家伙在当时就被「黑暗」给吞掉了的话</font></p>
<p begin="10463900000t" end="10483900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那故事不就结束了吗</font></p>
<p begin="10484700000t" end="10503500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不不  不是这样的</font></p>
<p begin="10505200000t" end="10514300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">认真听吾说啊</font></p>
<p begin="10518100000t" end="10563500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾说的可是「他几乎整个人都被吞进去了」</font></p>
<p begin="10563500000t" end="10571100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是啊</font></p>
<p begin="10574000000t" end="10601500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以我才会有疑问啊  那不就…</font></p>
<p begin="10601500000t" end="10606500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">几乎</font></p>
<p begin="10608600000t" end="10624000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说还留下了一部分</font></p>
<p begin="10641100000t" end="10656600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">右手腕留了下来</font></p>
<p begin="10669100000t" end="10674900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">手腕？</font></p>
<p begin="10678200000t" end="10702400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾不是说了他是先被吞进去的吗</font></p>
<p begin="10705800000t" end="10719100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后当他被吞没的时候</font></p>
<p begin="10719100000t" end="10762100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他简直如同抓住救命稻草一般抓住了吾的手腕</font></p>
<p begin="10769600000t" end="10786700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就像这样紧紧地</font></p>
<p begin="10800500000t" end="10840900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾和他的手腕一起飞去了南极</font></p>
<p begin="10857600000t" end="10917200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果被留在南极的就只有吾一个人和他的手腕</font></p>
<p begin="10926800000t" end="10938100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">留下的…</font></p>
<p begin="10940200000t" end="10953500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只是孤零零的一个吾</font></p>
<p begin="10959800000t" end="10988600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">时隔百年  吾又一次有了这种感觉</font></p>
<p begin="10995200000t" end="11021100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾被巨大的孤独感所包围</font></p>
<p begin="11025300000t" end="11088200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这和吾刚刚遭遇了「黑暗」这一未知现象也是有关系的</font></p>
<p begin="11094900000t" end="11121200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽说不至于感到危险和不安</font></p>
<p begin="11123700000t" end="11136600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但至少吾感受到了威胁</font></p>
<p begin="11142000000t" end="11166600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以吾让他复活了</font></p>
<p begin="11170800000t" end="11191300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾造出了第一个眷属</font></p>
<p begin="11199600000t" end="11222500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是有种说法叫做「吊桥效应」吗</font></p>
<p begin="11225000000t" end="11256700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">人会把身在吊桥上时因恐惧而加速的心跳</font></p>
<p begin="11257600000t" end="11296800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">误认为是坠入爱河所产生的心动</font></p>
<p begin="11301800000t" end="11306800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说</font></p>
<p begin="11306800000t" end="11311800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（如果这么解释的话）</font></p>
<p begin="11311800000t" end="11330600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">当身处吊桥上或者其他环境下</font></p>
<p begin="11328500000t" end="11333500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（的确是一种很容易理解的现象）</font></p>
<p begin="11333500000t" end="11361000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">生命受到威胁的时候</font></p>
<p begin="11341000000t" end="11346000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不过那个「效果」）</font></p>
<p begin="11356800000t" end="11361800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（也可以有其他解释）</font></p>
<p begin="11363500000t" end="11383100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">生物就会本能地想要留下后代</font></p>
<p begin="11384800000t" end="11402700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因而会容易坠入爱河之类</font></p>
<p begin="11411900000t" end="11442300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">恋情还是爱情  家人或是眷属</font></p>
<p begin="11444800000t" end="11467400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那并不是这些感情所导致的现象</font></p>
<p begin="11471100000t" end="11483200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而是有着冲动性的</font></p>
<p begin="11478200000t" end="11483200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（汝可以表现得失望一点）</font></p>
<p begin="11485300000t" end="11503200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">无法被赞赏的理由</font></p>
<p begin="11492400000t" end="11497400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（在这里）</font></p>
<p begin="11513700000t" end="11528700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只是因为心灵变得脆弱了而已</font></p>
<p begin="11536200000t" end="11581200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾大口地咬在那家伙的右手腕上  吸了他的血</font></p>
<p begin="11589600000t" end="11627100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是为了进食  而是为了制造眷属吸了他的血</font></p>
<p begin="11637100000t" end="11648000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为讨厌孤独</font></p>
<p begin="11652600000t" end="11663800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以吾放弃了神的身份</font></p>
<p begin="11668400000t" end="11683800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">做回了吸血鬼</font></p>
<p begin="11723300000t" end="11794400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}今もずっとその声を覚えてるから</font></p>
<p begin="11723300000t" end="11794400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">现在我也记得你的声音</font></p>
<p begin="11889300000t" end="11915400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日走った道に</font></p>
<p begin="11889300000t" end="11915400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子走过的路</font></p>
<p begin="11917400000t" end="11943600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}あの日見上げた空に</font></p>
<p begin="11917400000t" end="11943600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">那些日子仰望的天空</font></p>
<p begin="11946000000t" end="11996100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}二度と返らない時を重ねてる</font></p>
<p begin="11946000000t" end="11996100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">无法回去的曾经反复叠加</font></p>
<p begin="12001700000t" end="12028100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}君は笑うだろうか</font></p>
<p begin="12001700000t" end="12028100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你恐怕会笑我吧</font></p>
<p begin="12029400000t" end="12056000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}少し怒るだろうね</font></p>
<p begin="12029400000t" end="12056000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">会有一丝生气吧</font></p>
<p begin="12058200000t" end="12113300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}こんな諦め悪い僕のことを</font></p>
<p begin="12058200000t" end="12113300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">我就是这么一个无法死心的人</font></p>
<p begin="12119800000t" end="12150200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}何度でも</font></p>
<p begin="12119800000t" end="12150200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">一次又一次</font></p>
<p begin="12153300000t" end="12209600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}迂闊に願う可能性を清書して  （いつまでも）</font></p>
<p begin="12153300000t" end="12209600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">将那些恍惚间许愿的可能性整理起来  （直到永远）</font></p>
<p begin="12209600000t" end="12255300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}まだ迷いそうに騙されてたくて</font></p>
<p begin="12209600000t" end="12255300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">都想这样迷茫地被自己所欺骗</font></p>
<p begin="12259700000t" end="12310900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}だから「どうかせめて」なんて思う心は</font></p>
<p begin="12259700000t" end="12310900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">因此许下这些愿望的心情</font></p>
<p begin="12312200000t" end="12345800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}一時的な感傷だって</font></p>
<p begin="12312200000t" end="12345800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">这些暂时的感伤</font></p>
<p begin="12347800000t" end="12370500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}許せばいい</font></p>
<p begin="12347800000t" end="12370500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">只要认可就好</font></p>
<p begin="12372400000t" end="12400900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}だからそうさ君がやっと</font></p>
<p begin="12372400000t" end="12400900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">因此请让我对你说</font></p>
<p begin="12402200000t" end="12423700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}絶望の先で</font></p>
<p begin="12402200000t" end="12423700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">在我绝望的时候</font></p>
<p begin="12425600000t" end="12515600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}くれた日々に偽りなんてないと言ってあげよう</font></p>
<p begin="12425600000t" end="12515600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">你曾给我带来的那些日子没有虚假</font></p>
<p begin="12532500000t" end="12575400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398"><font face="DFGHSMincho-W5" size="36" color="#f6d440">{\an8}忘れないで</font></p>
<p begin="12532500000t" end="12575400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399"><font face="STZhongsong" size="39" color="#f6d440">不要将我忘记</font></p>
<p begin="12631800000t" end="12647700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  你成功了吗</font></p>
<p begin="12652300000t" end="12662500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾失败了</font></p>
<p begin="12664600000t" end="12677400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">失…失败？</font></p>
<p begin="12679700000t" end="12717100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和吾想的一样  初代怪异杀手复活了</font></p>
<p begin="12720900000t" end="12764500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过  说不定是因为他的内心不如汝强大吧</font></p>
<p begin="12767900000t" end="12807100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在回想起来  说不定是因为吾关心的不够吧</font></p>
<p begin="12812900000t" end="12859300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">记得你说他自己冲到了太阳下  化为灰烬了啊</font></p>
<p begin="12863000000t" end="12881500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错  他自杀了</font></p>
<p begin="12878900000t" end="12881400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（无法避免）</font></p>
<p begin="12881400000t" end="12883900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（没能避免）</font></p>
<p begin="12883900000t" end="12887600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（他的自杀）</font></p>
<p begin="12889900000t" end="12918300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这是大约九成的吸血鬼最终都会选择的</font></p>
<p begin="12919500000t" end="12946200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">普通得不能再普通的死法…</font></p>
<p begin="12971500000t" end="12975200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（燃烧  再生）</font></p>
<p begin="12975200000t" end="12979000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（燃烧  再生）</font></p>
<p begin="12979000000t" end="12982700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（燃烧  再生）</font></p>
<p begin="12984400000t" end="12988100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（直到彻底化为灰烬为止）</font></p>
<p begin="13011900000t" end="13035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那时你没去救他吗</font></p>
<p begin="13039300000t" end="13075700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就像春假时你救了跑去太阳下的我那样</font></p>
<p begin="13080500000t" end="13091500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾没法救他</font></p>
<p begin="13095500000t" end="13141500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而且当时的吾也不太明白他为什么要这么做</font></p>
<p begin="13145400000t" end="13196600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说回来  直到他选择自杀为止  吾还和他交流了很多</font></p>
<p begin="13199400000t" end="13239700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过当时吾和他之间的关系已经几乎破裂了</font></p>
<p begin="13245400000t" end="13257900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这是无计可施的</font></p>
<p begin="13261500000t" end="13269700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">破裂是指？</font></p>
<p begin="13269700000t" end="13271300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（答非所问）</font></p>
<p begin="13271300000t" end="13273800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这简直是答非所问）</font></p>
<p begin="13275800000t" end="13301500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说白了就是他生气了</font></p>
<p begin="13302700000t" end="13347500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">初代怪异杀手对于吾把他变成吸血鬼这件事生气了</font></p>
<p begin="13356400000t" end="13358500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（居然不是「神」而是「鬼」）</font></p>
<p begin="13358500000t" end="13361400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（「吸血鬼」的身份——暴露了）</font></p>
<p begin="13362500000t" end="13381000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从一只断手上获得了新生</font></p>
<p begin="13383800000t" end="13432700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">重生为吸血鬼的初代怪异杀手</font></p>
<p begin="13435000000t" end="13451500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对吾说的第一句话是</font></p>
<p begin="13455100000t" end="13505900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">「你这怪物  居然骗了我们」</font></p>
<p begin="13521900000t" end="13550900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他对吾怒吼道「这全都是你害的吗」</font></p>
<p begin="13553300000t" end="13586700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与其说是怒吼  不如说更接近责问吧</font></p>
<p begin="13590100000t" end="13624500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他甚至对吾说吾会受到天谴什么的</font></p>
<p begin="13627400000t" end="13669900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是说他把包括失踪在内的所有事情都怪罪到你头上了吗</font></p>
<p begin="13673000000t" end="13699800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他甚至认为那片「黑暗」也是你动的手脚</font></p>
<p begin="13700400000t" end="13702500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（规模不一样）</font></p>
<p begin="13704700000t" end="13722900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后你是怎么做的呢</font></p>
<p begin="13727300000t" end="13737000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">先不管动机如何</font></p>
<p begin="13739500000t" end="13757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你毫无疑问是救了他一命</font></p>
<p begin="13760700000t" end="13791900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但却被他这么说  心里肯定不太好受吧</font></p>
<p begin="13793700000t" end="13817300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不  那倒没有</font></p>
<p begin="13820700000t" end="13846900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过要解开误会实在太麻烦了</font></p>
<p begin="13848200000t" end="13865300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以吾就随他说去了</font></p>
<p begin="13868500000t" end="13915800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾想他虽然现在有些混乱  但一定很快就会冷静下来吧</font></p>
<p begin="13929100000t" end="13930700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（要说不想让他死去的想法)</font></p>
<p begin="13930700000t" end="13932400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真的）</font></p>
<p begin="13932400000t" end="13933700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（完全）</font></p>
<p begin="13933700000t" end="13935300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（一丝都没有）</font></p>
<p begin="13935300000t" end="13937800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（那是不可能的）</font></p>
<p begin="13948700000t" end="13951200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这家伙要是那种女人的话）</font></p>
<p begin="13951200000t" end="13954900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（我就不会像这样活着了）</font></p>
<p begin="13954900000t" end="13958300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不会作为半个吸血鬼——而活着）</font></p>
<p begin="13972500000t" end="13990000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但他并没有冷静下来</font></p>
<p begin="13992300000t" end="14010000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">混乱  甚至精神错乱</font></p>
<p begin="14011800000t" end="14032100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">与吾彻底翻脸</font></p>
<p begin="14034300000t" end="14053500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">最终选择了自杀</font></p>
<p begin="14058600000t" end="14081000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">他一边对吾说着怨恨的话语</font></p>
<p begin="14083800000t" end="14107100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">其中还夹杂着后悔和抱怨</font></p>
<p begin="14109500000t" end="14143800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后当着吾的面冲进了阳光下</font></p>
<p begin="14146500000t" end="14153700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">——死了</font></p>
<p begin="14162100000t" end="14174200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾既没能阻止他</font></p>
<p begin="14175800000t" end="14187700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也没能救他</font></p>
<p begin="14192600000t" end="14228700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">明明在抵达南极后吾都把真名告诉他了</font></p>
<p begin="14233000000t" end="14296500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果他只在临自杀前叫了吾「姬丝秀忒」一次</font></p>
<p begin="14314700000t" end="14345300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">即使如此  他还是叫你「姬丝秀忒」</font></p>
<p begin="14350700000t" end="14379900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既不是「刃下心」  也不是「雅赛劳拉莉昂」</font></p>
<p begin="14385100000t" end="14406100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而是和我一样叫你「姬丝秀忒」</font></p>
<p begin="14411800000t" end="14418900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样一来…</font></p>
<p begin="14425800000t" end="14441100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后他就死了</font></p>
<p begin="14446100000t" end="14465500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为吸血鬼是不死之身</font></p>
<p begin="14467100000t" end="14500200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以准确地说应该是「毁灭」了吧</font></p>
<p begin="14502300000t" end="14512700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之他死了</font></p>
<p begin="14517100000t" end="14571100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">作为遗物他留下了费尽全部心血打造的妖刀心渡的复制品</font></p>
<p begin="14579100000t" end="14604800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">反正他是为了杀死吾才去打造的吧</font></p>
<p begin="14610300000t" end="14653100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">直到那时为止  吾只是无意中没有制造眷属而已</font></p>
<p begin="14654100000t" end="14697700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">并不是固执地坚持着单身主义</font></p>
<p begin="14702300000t" end="14740500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不过当吾目送着他那冒着青色火焰的尸体逐渐消逝</font></p>
<p begin="14742500000t" end="14769900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾就发誓再也不去制造眷属</font></p>
<p begin="14773100000t" end="14815400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再也不因摄取养分之外的目的去吸人血</font></p>
<p begin="14821500000t" end="14830600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾对神发了誓</font></p>
<p begin="14836500000t" end="14864100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">至少我是笑不出来</font></p>
<p begin="14868900000t" end="14890300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说得好听点  我甚至无法佩服她</font></p>
<p begin="14896100000t" end="14915500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为结果直到最终</font></p>
<p begin="14922100000t" end="14953900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">她无论是作为「神」还是「吸血鬼」</font></p>
<p begin="14957800000t" end="14981800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">都无法和人类「好好相处」</font></p>
<p begin="15000100000t" end="15012300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这段鬼的独白</font></p>
<p begin="15018200000t" end="15041000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">距今四百年前的故事</font></p>
<p begin="15047500000t" end="15074200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就这样以悲伤的结局划上了句号</font></p>
<p begin="15111400000t" end="15119800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493"><font face="@FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}火怜DaZe！</font></p>
<p begin="15111700000t" end="15118400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">火怜Da☆Ze！</font></p>
<p begin="15119800000t" end="15126500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">月火Da☆Yo！</font></p>
<p begin="15119800000t" end="15127300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496"><font face="@FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an7}月火DaYo！</font></p>
<p begin="15127300000t" end="15146900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}我们是Fire Sisters！</font></p>
<p begin="15128000000t" end="15146900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">两个人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！</font></p>
<p begin="15146900000t" end="15231500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}变成神的方法？</font></p>
<p begin="15146900000t" end="15231500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle500"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}是不是理解错了</font></p>
<p begin="15150000000t" end="15178500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle501"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">十二个人合在一起就是Fire Sister Princess Da☆Ze！</font></p>
<p begin="15178500000t" end="15198800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle502"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之先把斧乃木妹妹拉进来再说</font></p>
<p begin="15198800000t" end="15209000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle503"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">预告篇Quiz！</font></p>
<p begin="15209000000t" end="15215400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle504"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">Quiz！</font></p>
<p begin="15216400000t" end="15237800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle505"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">『奥兹国历险记』  读过没有啊？</font></p>
<p begin="15231500000t" end="15315000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle506"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}好厉害！快给我们看看！</font></p>
<p begin="15237800000t" end="15256500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle507"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">读过读过  都快读烂了</font></p>
<p begin="15256500000t" end="15289600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle508"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一起旅行的伙伴不是狮子稻草人和铁皮机器人么</font></p>
<p begin="15289600000t" end="15304600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle509"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没错啊  传说中的御三家啊</font></p>
<p begin="15305800000t" end="15325000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle510"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">稻草人和机器人的设定不觉得有点重复吗？</font></p>
<p begin="15315000000t" end="15400000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle511"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}激动激动</font></p>
<p begin="15315000000t" end="15400000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle512"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}哎！交给我了？！</font></p>
<p begin="15315000000t" end="15400000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle513"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}这事就交给你了…</font></p>
<p begin="15326000000t" end="15336900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle514"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">两个都是人型</font></p>
<p begin="15336900000t" end="15372400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle515"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就算稻草人当不了机器人  但是机器人也可以当稻草人啊</font></p>
<p begin="15373200000t" end="15387200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle516"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">稻草人真是没存在感啊</font></p>
<p begin="15387200000t" end="15403200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle517"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不管是在旅行途中还是在田野里</font></p>
<p begin="15405000000t" end="15433600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle518"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">想要寻找的东西是心和大脑  也有点重复</font></p>
<p begin="15433600000t" end="15452000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle519"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">二者合二为一的概率恐怕会很高啊</font></p>
<p begin="15452000000t" end="15482400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle520"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果这么说的话  狮子和托托的设定貌似也有点重复</font></p>
<p begin="15486800000t" end="15506800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle521"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">下集  鬼物语  第三话</font></p>
<p begin="15507800000t" end="15521200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle522"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">忍与时间  其三</font></p>
<p begin="15516000000t" end="15605200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle523"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}没有成神</font></p>
<p begin="15516000000t" end="15605200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle524"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}成佛了！</font></p>
<p begin="15523300000t" end="15545000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle525"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样一来真应该好好推敲一下队长的设定了</font></p>
<p begin="15545000000t" end="15549600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle526"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">奥兹</font></p>
<p begin="15549600000t" end="15566800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle527"><font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">奥兹又不是女主角的名字</font></p>
